An Act relative to reprecincting.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General Court assembled, and by the authority
of the same, as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Section 9A of chapter 9 of the General Laws, as appearing in the 2020
2 Official Edition, is hereby amended by inserting before the first paragraph the following
3 paragraph:-
4 For the purposes of this section “decennial division” shall mean the decennial division of
5 congressional, representative, senatorial and councillor districts as set forth in sections 1 through
6 7A, inclusive, of chapter 54.
7 SECTION 2. Said section 9A of said chapter 9, as so appearing, is hereby amended by
8 adding the following 7 paragraphs:-
9 The commission shall not approve the division of any city or town into wards and
10 precincts as required by chapter 54 until the final approval by the governor of the enacted
11 decennial division.
